{"tid":626275,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有毒無害] 褐色煙霧罩天！河南鋁企洩數百公斤濃硝酸","createTime":"2018-04-12T03:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T04:47:54.000Z","uid":54337,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a988574b0b5df79494ec27cda4d7c2958f6657e2","tid":626275,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:40:20.000Z","msg":"褐色煙霧罩天！河南鋁企洩數百公斤濃硝酸<br />\n<br />\n河南三門峽一家鋁業公司周三（11日）發生濃硝酸洩漏事件，現場被褐色的煙霧籠罩。有關人員到場利用噴水稀釋、鹼液中和等方式控制煙霧，約45分鐘後完成處置，事故中無人傷亡。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事發於當天下午4時15分，涉事的三門峽聯利新材料有限公司有濃硝酸儲罐發生洩漏。三門峽市環保及安監部門到場勘察，發現洩漏的硝酸約數百公斤，不過周邊並無環境敏感區。經處置後，現場已沒有再產生黃褐色煙霧。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180412/photo/bkncn-20180412094258889-0412_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180412101237\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180412%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180412094258889-0412_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180412101237&h=2066bea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毒霧兆豐年<br />\n妖氣賀登基"},{"pid":"5f234c8d3ad314e37275c5e8f28650d82a74ba1b","tid":626275,"uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:44:44.000Z","msg":"齋睇圖以為係敘利亞用化武現場"},{"pid":"1734289aaab78a5c62cf2029739ad1ec1f6d6c0c","tid":626275,"uid":22926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"好夢幻喎"},{"pid":"c95fcaf89867b3429b24cf6308b2027423c73650","tid":626275,"uid":174601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> filter都唔洗用"},{"pid":"46cc8bd9cf39b72bf2224217387e91590c69c373","tid":626275,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"幾濃先有咁啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/n